            "title": "设置shoka主题",
            "date_published": "2025-07-18T19:52:40.000Z",
            "content_html": "<ul>\n<li><span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL2FtZWhpbWUvaGV4by10aGVtZS1zaG9rYT90YWI9cmVhZG1lLW92LWZpbGU=\">shoka-theme</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"配置shoka主题\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#配置shoka主题\">#</a> 配置 shoka 主题</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>在 <em>_config.yml</em> 文件中设置  <code>theme：shoka</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"问题排查\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#问题排查\">#</a> 问题排查</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>执行 <code>hexo g</code>  时提示如下错误</p>\n  <figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Prism&#x27;s Diff Highlight plugin requires the Diff language definition (prism-diff.js).Make sure the language definition is loaded or use Prism&#x27;s Autoloader plugin.</span><br><span class=\"line\">ERROR Process failed: languages/README.md</span><br><span class=\"line\">TypeError: pangu.spacing is not a function</span><br><span class=\"line\">    at /home/yangjian/Workspace/Project/blogs/node_modules/hexo-renderer-multi-markdown-it/lib/renderer/markdown-it-prism/index.js:42:33</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><code>Prism's Diff Highlight</code>  插件缺少 Diff 语言定义，你需要加载 prism-diff.js，否则 Diff 语法高亮无法使用。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>解决方法：在 index.js 里添加加载 Diff 语言的代码：</li>\n</ul>\n <figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 在 require(&#x27;prismjs/components/&#x27;) 后面加上</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">loadLanguages</span>([<span class=\"string\">&#x27;diff&#x27;</span>]);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>TypeError: pangu.spacing is not a function</code> ，说明 pangu 包没有正确导出 spacing 方法。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>解决方法：将  <code>pangu.spacing()</code>  修改为  <code>pangu.spacingText()</code></li>\n</ul>\n <figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">env.<span class=\"property\">content</span> = pangu.<span class=\"title function_\">spacingText</span>(env.<span class=\"property\">content</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n",
            "tags": [
                "hexo"
            ]
        },
